.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-today-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-mazagon-dock-rec-crude-oil-123121100067_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pics%3A%20China%20Carves%20Into%20Bhutan%20With%20Outposts%2C%20Villages%20Despite%20Talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOngoing%20border%20talks%20between%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20to%20formally%20demarcate%20their%20boundary%20have%20not%20prevented%20Beijing%20from%20continuing%20unsanctioned%20construction%20activity%20in%20North%20Bhutan's%20Jakarlung%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20images%20of%20this%20region%2C%20the%20sharpest%20to%20be%20released%20so%20far%2C%20suggest%20that%20Thimphu%20may%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20accept%20the%20fait%20accompli%20presented%20by%20the%20Chinese%20in%20this%20area%20which%20lies%2050%20kilometres%20from%20Bhutan's%20Eastern%20border%20with%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20case%20of%20China%20making%20a%20claim%20to%20an%20area%2C%20based%20on%20earlier%20grazing%20practices%20by%20herders%2C%20that%20is%20very%20recent%20and%20without%20precedent%20-%20and%20then%20unilaterally%20seizing%20the%20territory%20and%20settling%20it%20with%20villages%2C%20military%20barracks%20and%20outposts%2C''%20according%20to%20Professor%20Robert%20Barnett%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20Tibetan%20history%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Oriental%20and%20African%20Studies%20(SOAS)%20at%20the%20University%20of%20London.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Jakarlung%20adjoins%20the%20Beyul%20Khenpajong%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20cultural%20and%20religious%20area%20for%20the%20Bhutanese.%20So%20this%20case%20represents%20China%20making%20a%20very%20recent%2C%20doubtful%20claim%20about%20an%20area%20that%20is%20of%20great%20cultural%20significance%20to%20a%20far%20less%20powerful%20neighbour%2C%20knowing%20that%20neighbour%20has%20few%20if%20any%20options%20as%20to%20its%20response.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20in%20