20sheer%20scale%20of%20this%20developmental%20activity%20emphasises%20that%20these%20villages%20are%20not%20merely%20isolated%20outposts%20but%20rather%20integral%20components%20forming%20a%20comprehensive%20ecosystem%20that%20supports%20China's%20territorial%20ambitions%2C%20further%20contributing%20to%20the%20Sinicization%20of%20the%20Bhutanese%20landscape%2C''%20says%20Damien%20Symon%2C%20who%20has%20written%20extensively%20about%20the%20Chinese%20intrusions%20in%20the%20East%20and%20West%20of%20Bhutan.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%20%5BWith%20inputs%20from%20Damien%20Symon%5D%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%20%5BWith%20inputs%20from%20Damien%20Symon%5D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6tm902so_slide-2-_625x300_11_December_23.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMap%20location%20of%20construction%20activity%20identified%20in%20this%20story%20with%20other%20areas%20of%20disputed%20Chinese%20construction%20activity%20on%20Bhutanese%20territory%20highlighted.%20(With%20inputs%20from%20Damien%20Symon)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20images%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Bhutan%20has%20stepped%20up%20ties%20with%20China%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20end%20Chinese%20incursions%20into%20its%20territory%20once%20and%20for%20all.%20%C2%A0In%20October%20this%20year%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20Tandi%20Dorji%20travelled%20to%20Beijing%2C%20a%20first%20for%20Bhutan.%20%C2%A0That%20same%20month%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Lotay%20Tshering%20told%20The%20Hindu%2C%20''We%20hope%20to%20see%20a%20line%20being%20drawn-%20this%20side%20Bhutan%20and%20that%20side%20China.%20We%20don't%20have%20that%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Before%20and%20after%20images%20of%20Chinese%20construction%20activity%20in%20the%20Jakarlung%20Valley%20shows%20a%20second%20enclave%20having%20been%20constructed%20by%20December%202023.%20(high%20res%3A%20here)%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Before%20and%20after%20images%20of%20Chinese%20construction%20activity%20in%20the%20Jakarlung%20Valley%20shows%20a%20second%20enclave%20having%20been%20constructed%20by%20December%202023.%20(high%20res%3A%20here)%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6blcki1g_china-settlement-maxar-_625x300_11_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20and%20after%20images%20of%20Chinese%20construction%20activity%20in%20the%20Jakarlung%20Valley%20shows%20a%20second%20enclave%20having%20been%20constructed%20by%20December%202023.%20(high%20res%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fglkb0org_china-settlement-maxar-hd-_625x300_11_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20in%20his%20interview%20to%20The%20Hindu%2C%20Tshering%20did%20not%20reject%20the%20possibility%20of%20Beijing%20and%20Thimphu%20agreeing%20to%20a%20land%20swap%20-%20where%20territory%20in%20areas%20including%20Jakarlung%2C%20described%20in%20this%20report%2C%20could%20be%20exchanged%20if%20China%20were%20to%20give%20up%20its%20claim%20to%20the%20Doklam%20plateau%20which%20lies%20further%20to%20the%20south.%20In%20November%2C%20Bhutan's%20King%20Jigme%20Khesar%20Nangyel%20Wangchuk%20visited%20India%20on%20an%20official%20visit.%20%C2%A0While%20details%20of%20the%20ongoing%20border%20negotiations%20were%20not%20spelt%20out%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20which%20was%20released%2C%20both%20sides%20''held%20discussions%20on%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20bilateral%20cooperation%20and%20regional%20and%20global%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20India%20and%20China%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20tense%20two-month-long%20standoff%20in%20Doklam%20when%20Indian%20troops%20physically%20prevented%20the%20extension%20of%20an%20illegal%20Chinese%20road%20in%20the%20area.%20%C2%A0Mr.%20Tshering%20did%2C%20however%2C%20confirm%20that%20''it%20will%20be%20to%20Bhutan's%20interest%20to%20make%20sure%20both%20the%20parties%20%5BIndia%20and%20China%5D%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20decisions%20we%20make''%20in%20the%20border%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrrespective%20of%20any%20outcome%2C%20''India%20may%20be%20concerned%20by%20the%20precedent%20that%20Jakarlung%20sets%20for%20China's%20willingness%20to%20abrogate%20treaty%20obligations%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20border%20disputes%2C''%20says%20Robert%20Barnett.%20''China%20signed%20a%20formal%20agreement%20with%20Bhutan%20in%201998%20not%20to%20alter%20the%20status%20quo%20in%20disputed%20areas.%20%C2%A0In%20occupying%20and%20settling%20Jakarlung%2C%20it%20violated%20that%20agreement.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20immediate%20concerns%20over%20Chinese%20expansion%20within%20Bhutanese%20territory%20also%20extend%20to%20the%20Amu%20Chu%20river%20valley%20which%20lies%20directly%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Doklam%20plateau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-doklam-standoff-bhutan-pms-china-comment-raises-concern-in-india-3900017%5C%22%3EIn%20Doklam%20Standoff%2C%20Bhutan%20PM's%20China%20Comment%20Raises%20Concern%20In%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Doklam%20standoff%2C%20China%20has%20constructed%20at%20least%20three%20villages%20along%20the%20valley.%20%C2%A0Any%20further%20Chinese%20extension%20South%20would%20raise%20alarm%20bells%20in%20New%20Delhi%20since%20that%20would%20mean%20a%20Chinese%20presence%20close%20to%20the%20Siliguri%20Corridor%2C%20the%20narrow%20corridor%20that%20connects%20India's%20Northeast%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20%C2%A0The%20Indian%20Army%20has%2C%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20government%20that%20China%20is%20approaching%20a%20red%20line%20that%20it%20should%20never%20be%20allowed%20to%20cross.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20use%20of%20what%20India's%20first%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%2C%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bsalami-slicing%26quot%3B%20of%20territory%20has%20been%20a%20standard%20tactic%20for%20all%20of%20its%20territorial%20expansion%20plans%20-%20from%20converting%20shoals%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Seas%20to%20full-fledged%20military%20outposts%20to%20pushing%20across%20multiple%20points%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''In%20May%202020%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20advanced%20in%20five%20areas%2C%20but%20in%20that%20case%2C%20India%20strongly%20reacted%20after%20a%20few%20days%2C''%20explains%20Claude%20Arpi%2C%20the%20renowned%20Tibetologist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''In%20Bhutan's%20case%2C%20the%20Royal%20Bhutan%20Army%20does%20not%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20react%20and%20push%20the%20PLA%20or%20Border%20Defence%20Force%20back%20or%20even%20stop%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20new%20villages.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20greater%20concern%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20which%20in%20the%20past%20was%20a%20net%20guarantor%20of%20security%20for%20Bhutan%2C%20the%20ongoing%20talks%20could%20result%20in%20a%20profound%20geo-strategic%20realignment%20in%20the%20area.%20%C2%A0''Bhutan%20is%20slowly%20shifting%20towards%20the%20strategic%20orbit%20of%20China%20and%20there%20is%20not%20much%20that%20India%20can%20do%2C%20except%20if%20a%20new%20security%20agreement%20is%20signed%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Thimphu%2C''%20says%20Arpi.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It%20is%20a%20difficult%20situation%20for%20Delhi%20and%20for%20the%20King%20of%20Bhutan.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702267440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fj1afgjbo_china-settlement-maxar-_625x300_11_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdespite-ongoing-talks-china-carves-into-north-bhutan-with-outposts-villages-4652302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ongoing%20border%20talks%20between%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20to%20formally%20d