20children%20who%20are%20all%20sick%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mohammed%20Daloul%2C%2038%2C%20who%20fled%20there%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Collapsing'%20health%20system%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20estimates%20that%201.9%20million%20of%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes%20--%20roughly%20half%20of%20them%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20had%20urged%20people%20to%20seek%20refuge%20in%20the%20south%2C%20but%20after%20expanding%20the%20war%20to%20include%20southern%20targets%2C%20there%20were%20few%20safe%20places%20for%20civilians%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHumanitarian%20organisations%20continued%20to%20press%20Israel%20for%20greater%20protection%20of%20civilians%20in%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMapping%20software%20deployed%20by%20Israel's%20army%20to%20try%20to%20reduce%20non-combatant%20deaths%20was%20condemned%20as%20inadequate%20Sunday%20by%20Lynn%20Hastings%2C%20UN%20humanitarian%20coordinator%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20unilateral%20declaration%20by%20an%20occupying%20power%20that%20patches%20of%20land%20where%20there%20is%20no%20infrastructure%2C%20food%2C%20water%2C%20health%20care%2C%20or%20hygiene%20are%20'safe%20zones'%20does%20not%20mean%20they%20are%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%2014%20of%20Gaza's%2036%20hospitals%20are%20functioning%20at%20any%20capacity%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20Nations'%20humanitarian%20agency%20OCHA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGaza's%20health%20system%20is%20on%20its%20knees%20and%20collapsing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20World%20Health%20Organization%20chief%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%2C%20as%20the%20agency%20called%20for%20immediate%2C%20unimpeded%20aid%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20army%20chief%20Herzi%20Halevi%20said%20Sunday%20his%20troops%20were%20using%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20force%