ectronic-devices-ats-arrests-activist-couple-for-alleged-naxal-links%5C%22%3Ewho%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police%20in%20October%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20charges%20of%20alleged%20Maoist%20links%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%20in%20prison%20a%20week%20after%20a%20court%20in%20Lucknow%20dismissed%20her%20plea%20for%20bail%20on%20medical%20grounds%20of%20a%20high-risk%20pregnancy%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20had%20on%20October%2018%20arrested%20Anita%20Aazad%20alias%20Prabha%20and%20her%20husband%20and%20fellow%20activist%20Brijesh%20Kushwaha%2C%20more%20than%20four%20years%20after%20the%20couple%20had%20been%20questioned%20for%20suspected%20Maoist%20links.%20While%20the%20police%20did%20not%20arrest%20the%20couple%20in%202019%20for%20want%20of%20physical%20evidence%2C%20Kushwaha%20and%20Prabha%20were%20arrested%20in%20October%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20examination%20and%20data%20extraction%20of%20electronic%20devices%20seized%20from%20them%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabha%20has%20been%20lodged%20in%20Lucknow%20district%20jail%20since%20October%2020.%20On%20December%209%20evening%2C%20Prabha%2C%20who%20was%20four-and-a-half%20months%20pregnant%2C%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20women%E2%80%99s%20government%20hospital%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20her%20medical%20reports%20show.%20The%20miscarriage%20was%20officially%20recorded%20at%209.15%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20under%20immense%20mental%20stress.%20I%20cannot%20even%20express%20it.%20I%20had%20taken%20a%20big%20risk%20in%20getting%20pregnant%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prabha%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20her%20hospital%20bed.%20The%20call%20was%20facilitated%20by%20a%20family%20member%20attending%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20second%20miscarriage%20Prabha%20suffered%20this%20year.%20As%20she%20suffers%20from%20a%20hyper%20thyroid%20condition%2C%20which%20contributes%20to%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20pregnancy%2C%20her%20family%20members%20said%2C%20citing%20her%20medical%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18194314%2Fimage-1403.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18194314%2Fimage-1403.png%20628w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18194314%2Fimage-1403-300x144.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22302%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBrijesh%20Kushwaha%20and%20Prabha.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Entirely%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20fault%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabha%20alleged%20that%20the%20doctor%20treating%20her%20inside%20the%20prison%20did%20not%20show%20the%20required%20urgency%20to%20send%20her%20to%20the%20district%20hospital%20for%20treatment%20when%20she%20suffered%20abdomen%20pain.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20entirely%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20fault%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20spotting%20(a%20term%20for%20vaginal%20bleeding)%20had%20started%20on%20Friday%20night%20but%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20district%20hospital%20only%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20Tiwari%2C%20Lucknow%20district%20jail%20superintendent%2C%20denied%20Prabha%E2%80%99s%20charge%20of%20negligence%20and%20said%20she%20had%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20district%20hospital%2C%20which%20was%20well-equipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20said%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20medical%20cause%20of%20the%20miscarriage%20could%20be%20made%20only%20after%20the%20district%20hospital%20submitted%20their%20official%20report.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20her%20interpretation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Prabha%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20not%20received%20any%20complaint%20or%20adverse%20report%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kushwaha%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20Mazdoor%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Manch%20of%20Deoria%2C%20Prabha%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20outfit%20Savitri%20Bai%20Phule%20Sangarsh%20Samiti.%20Kushwaha%20completed%20M.A%20Sanskrit%20from%20Deoria%20and%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20Inquilabi%20Chhatra%20Sabha%20during%20his%20student%20days.%20He%20met%20Prabha%20while%20working%20in%20Bilaspur%20in%20Chhatisgarh%20in%202006%20and%20the%20two%20married%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20had%20in%20October%20said%20it%20arrested%20Kushwaha%20from%20his%20native%20place%20in%20Deoria%20in%20East%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20while%20Prabha%20was%20arrested%20from%20her%20maternal%20house%20in%20Raipur%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20where%20she%20had%20intended%20to%20rest%20during%20the%20period%20of%20her%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20faces%20charges%20under%20sections%20120B%2C%20121A%2C%20419%2C%20420%2C%20467%2C%20468%20and%20471%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20Sections%2013%2C%2018%20and%2038%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%20The%20ATS%20had%20claimed%20it%20found%20letters%20and%20literature%20from%20their%20electronic%20devices%20that%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20banned%20Maoist%20outfit%20PLGA%20(People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Guerilla%20Army)%20and%20CPI%20(Maoist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchildren-women-prisoners-india%5C%22%3EWhen%20%E2%80%98Bandi%E2%80%99%20Is%20Both%20a%20Game%20and%20Life%3A%20The%20Children%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Women%20Prisoners%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Won%E2%80%99t%20be%20proper%20to%20grant%20her%20bail%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabha%20applied%20for%20bail%20in%20a%20district%20court%20stating%20that%20she%20was%20falsely%20implicated%20by%20the%20ATS%20to%20show%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20work.%E2%80%9D%20There%20was%20no%20evidence%20linking%20her%20to%20any%20Maoist%20organisation%20or%20criminal%20organisation%2C%20she%20told%20court.%20Prabha%20also%20cited%20her%20pregnancy%20and%20medical%20condition%20while%20pleading%20for%20bail.%20She%20had%20then%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20she%20was%20four%20months%20pregnant%20and%20suffered%20from%20diabetes%20and%20hyper%20thyroid%20condition.%20%E2%80%9CDoctor%20has%20advised%20her%20full%20bedrest%20and%20proper%20diet%2C%20which%20are%20not%20possible%20in%20the%20jail%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20lawyer%20submitted%20in%20court%20in%20the%20bail%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%20Vivekananda%20Sharan%20Tripathi%2C%20special%20judge%20NIA%2FATS%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20rejected%20her%20bail%20plea%20saying%20that%20the%20allegations%20against%20her%20were%20%E2%80%9Cprima%20facie%20of%20a%20serious%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20not%20be%20proper%20to%20grant%20her%20bail%20merely%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20is%20pregnant%2C%E2%80%9D%20judge%20Tripathi%20said%20in%20his%20order%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20that%20two%20witnesses%20%E2%80%93%20Rajesh%20Gupta%20and%20Dinanath%20Nishad%20%E2%80%93%20in%20their%20statement%20under%20CrPC%20164%20had%20supported%20the%20allegations%20of%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20that%20the%20matter%20concerning%20the%20accused%20is%20anti-social%20and%20anti-national%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Findia-women-prisoners-rights%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTheir%2520menstrual%2520hygiene%2520was%2520one%2Cfood%2520provisioning%2520and%2520cooking%2520either.%5C%22%3EThe%20Lives%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Women%20Prisoners%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Maoist%20links%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20opposing%20her%20bail%2C%20the%20special%20public%20prosecutor%20arguing%20for%20the%20ATS%20said%20that%20during%20an%20analysis%20of%20a%20data%20extraction%20report%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20laptop%20they%20had%20found%20a%20typewritten%20letter%20in%20a%20word%20file%20linked%20to%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20The%20public%20prosecutor%20said%20Prabha%20had%20allegedly%20worked%20with%20a%20Maoist%20leader%20K.%20Srinivas%20alias%20Arvindji%2C%20who%20carried%20a%20bounty%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20in%20Chambal%2C%20and%20provided%20him%20shelter%20along%20with%20her%20other%20aides%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Maharajganj%20in%20East%20UP.%20The%20ATS%20accused%20Prabha%20of%20helping%20Arvindji%20conceal%20his%20identity%20and%20evade%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202019%2C%20while%20questioning%20the%20couple%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20FIR%20lodged%20on%20alleged%20Maoist%20links%2C%20the%20ATS%20had%20seized%20their%20electronic%20devices%20and%20sent%20them%20for%20examination%20and%20data%20extraction%20to%20an%20FSL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20in%20October%20said%20it%20found%20documents%20linked%20to%20Maoists%20after%20carrying%20out%20an%20%E2%80%9Cintensive%20analysis%20of%20the%20report%20packed%20with%20the%20complete%20extracted%20digital%20data%20received%20from%20the%20FSL%20this%20month.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ATS%20also%20claimed%20it%20recovered%20letters%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccomrades%20of%20CPI%20(Maoist)%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20references%20to%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%20from%20their%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20accused%20Kushwaha%20and%20Prabha%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20activities%E2%80%9D%20and%20spreading%20Communist%20ideology%20through%20the%20outfits%20run%20by%20them.%20When%20the%20ATS%20had%20raided%20their%20home%20in%202019%20and%20questioned%20them%2C%20it%20did%20not%20find%20any%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20material%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20which%20they%20were%20not%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20in%20the%20FIR%20suspected%20Maoists%20had%20been%20holding%20meetings%20in%20the%20states%20of%20UP%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20and%20were%20engaging%20in%20criminal%20conspiracy%20to%20instigate%20people%20for%20armed%20rebellion%20and%20making%20a%20plan%20for%20satta%20parivartan%20(change%20in%20government).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20had%20in%202019%20arrested%20two%20out%20of%20the%20seven%20persons%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20Manish%20Azad%20aka%20Manish%20Srivastava%20and%20his%20wife%20Anita%20Srivastava%20from%20their%20residence%20in%20Bhopal.%20The%20two%2C%20who%20have%20a%20record%20in%20translation%20and%20academic%20work%2C%20were%20later%20granted%20bail.%20Kushwaha%20and%20Prabha%20were%20among%20those%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20then%20conducted%20raids%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Deoria%20and%20Kushinagar%2C%20and%20also%20seized%20several%20electronic%20devices%20and%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20had%20earlier%20this%20year%20interrogated%20one%20of%20the%20co-accused%20in%20the%202019%20FIR%2C%20Manish%20Azad%2C%20as%20it%20conducted%20simultaneous%20searches%20at%20the%20residences%20and%20offices%20of%20several%20activists%2C%20including%20Manish%E2%80%99s%20sister%20and%20national%20secretary%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20Seema%20Azad%2C%20and%20students%20in%20various%20cities%20of%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20NIA%20said%20its%20raid%20was%20against%20suspects%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20attempts%20by%20leaders%20and%20cadres%20of%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20to%20revive%20the%20banned%20organization%20across%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702264689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F01091058%2F1-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanita-aazad-prabha-kushwaha-miscarriage-jail-medical-bail-maoist-link%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20arrested%20in%20October%20this%20year%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20examination%20and%20data%20extraction%20of%20electronic%20devices%20seized%20from%20them%20four%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanita-aazad-prabha-kushwaha-miscarriage-jail-medical-bail-maoist-link%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Good%20problem...'%3A%20Gavaskar%20on%20India's%20T20%20WC%20opening%20combination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702264679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105889144%2Cimgsize-58372.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-south-africa%2Fits-a-very-good-problem-sunil-gavaskar-on-indias-opening-combination-for-t20-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F105888773.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20preparations%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20are%20focusing%20on%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%2C%20with%20the%20BCCI%20selectors%20aiming%20to%20infuse%20youth%20into%20the%20squad%20to%20end%20India's%20ICC%20title%20drought%20since%202013.%20The%20South%20Africa%20Tour%20squad%20includes%20promising%20youngsters%20like%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20and%20Tilak%20Varma.%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20leads%20the%20T20I%20series%2C%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma%20taking%20a%20