-pose-shirtless-flaunt-buzzcuts-ahead-of-military-enlistment%2Farticleshow%2F105888986.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twinkle%20Khanna%20on%20eventually%20turning%2050%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702264386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105888876%2Cimgsize-27450.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftwinkle-khanna-opens-up-on-thoughts-surrounding-turning-50-says-it-triggered-an-existential-crisis%2Farticleshow%2F105888760.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105888760.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETwinkle%20Khanna%2C%20known%20for%20her%20articulate%20expression%2C%20delves%20into%20thoughts%20on%20turning%2050%2C%20sharing%20the%20societal%20challenges%20for%20women.%20In%20her%20Times%20of%20India%20column%2C%20she%20unveils%20a%20surprising%20revelation%20of%20zero%20testosterone%20levels%20from%20a%20blood%20test.%20Reflecting%20on%20an%20existential%20crisis%20triggered%20by%20the%20milestone%2C%20Twinkle%20contrasts%20societal%20expectations%20between%20men%20and%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftwinkle-khanna-opens-up-on-thoughts-surrounding-turning-50-says-it-triggered-an-existential-crisis%2Farticleshow%2F105888760.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Don't%20Want%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gambhir%20When%20Asked%20About%20Sreesanth%20'Fixer'%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3