%20Yet%2C%20you%20continue%20to%20engage%20in%20conflicts%20with%20every%20cricketer.%20What%20is%20the%20matter%20with%20you%3F%20All%20I%20did%20was%20smile%20and%20observe%2C%20and%20you%20labelled%20me%20a%20fixer%3F%20Seriously%3F%20Are%20you%20above%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3F%20You%20have%20no%20authority%20to%20speak%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20and%20say%20whatever%20you%20please.%20You%20even%20verbally%20abused%20the%20umpires%2C%20and%20yet%20you%20speak%20of%20smiling%3F%20You%20are%20an%20arrogant%20and%20utterly%20classless%20individual%20who%20lacks%20any%20form%20of%20respect%20for%20those%20who%20supported%20you.%20Until%20yesterday%2C%20I%20always%20held%20respect%20for%20you%20and%20your%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20wrote%20in%20the%20comments%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20you%20used%20the%20derogatory%20term%20%26quot%3Bfixer%26quot%3B%20not%20just%20once%2C%20but%20seven%20or%20eight%20times.%20You%20even%20resorted%20to%20using%20the%20F-word%20towards%20the%20umpires%20and%20myself%2C%20persistently%20trying%20to%20provoke%20me.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20experienced%20what%20I%20have%20endured%20would%20never%20forgive%20you.%20Deep%20down%2C%20you%20know%20that%20what%20you%20said%20and%20did%20was%20wrong.%20I'm%20sure%20even%20God%20won't%20forgive%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20didn't%20even%20come%20to%20the%20field%20after%20that...%20Come%20on%2C%20God%20is%20watching%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702264380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fs8dg621o_gambhir_625x300_07_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-dont-want-to-gautam-gambhir-when-asked-about-fixer-controversy-with-s-sreesanth-4652244%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20S%20Sreesanth%20'fixer'%20controversy%20during%20a%20charity%20event%20in%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22