2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChicken%20rice%20is%20Singapore's%20best-known%20dish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETian%20Tian's%20version%20has%20earned%20the%20praise%20of%20Gordon%20Ramsay%2C%20Anthony%20Bourdain%2C%20and%20the%20Michelin%20Guide.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20certainly%20lives%20up%20to%20the%20hype%20and%20is%20well%20worth%20the%20slightly%20higher%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHawker%20centers%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0or%20open-air%20food%20courts%20%E2%80%94%20are%20the%20core%20of%20Singapore's%20vibrant%20food%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Singapore%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20have%20been%20eating%20at%20hawker%20centers%20ever%20since.%20These%20casual%20dining%20spots%20found%20across%20the%20island%20offer%20delicious%2C%20inexpensive%20meals%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20Food%20Centre%2C%20located%20in%20Singapore's%20vibrant%20Chinatown%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%20It%20was%20opened%20in%201928%20and%20survived%20World%20War%20II%20and%20the%20Japanese%20occupation.%20Back%20then%2C%20dishes%20were%20served%20for%20as%20little%20as%20eight%20Singapore%20cents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20taken%20during%20Maxwell's%20early%20days%20show%20locals%20sitting%20on%20simple%20stools%20around%20circular%20tables.%20People%20can%20be%20seen%20lining%20up%20outside%20dozens%20of%20food%20carts.%20The%20ceilings%20were%20covered%20with%20metal%20scaffolding%2C%20and%20overhead%20fans%20hung%20from%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20space%20isn't%20all%20that%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20only%20eaten%20at%20Maxwell%20a%20handful%20of%20times%2C%20as%20I%20live%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20city%2C%20just%2010%20minutes%20away%20from%20another%20popular%20hawker%20center%20in%20eastern%20Singapore%2C%20and%20usually%20frequent%20that%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20Maxwell%20Food%20Center%20in%20No