F10201346%2Fsugarcane-farmer-in-a-queue-waiting-to-sell_Alamy_2HM25XN-1800x1201-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ruralvoice.in%2Flatest-news%2Fwheat-stock-limit-halved-e-auction-quantity-increased-to-4-lakh-tonnes.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-economics%2Findia-bans-exports-of-some-rice-explained-9004685%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fgovt-rules-out-lifting-ban-on-wheat-export%2Farticleshow%2F100450885.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-extends-restrictions-on-sugar-exports-until-further-orders-11697611475899.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epolicy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Findia-bans-onion-exports-till-march-next-year%2Farticleshow%2F105829256.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eactions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20centred%20on%20agricultural%20crops%2C%20two%20things%20(among%20many%20others)%20come%20out%20clear%3A%20(i)%20domestic%20food%20security%20is%20central%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20even%20above%20other%20priorities%20including%20energy%20security%3B%20and%20that%20(ii)%20two%20years%20of%20consecutive%20shocks%20from%20climate%20(high%20temperatures%20and%20sub-optimal%20rains)%20have%20turned%20tables%20of%20a%20food%20surplus%20nation%20into%20one%20which%20is%20scratching%20to%20achieve%20self-sufficiency.%20In%20this%20brief%20article%2C%20we%20analyse%20recent%20government%20decision%20on%20ethanol%20and%20how%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20and%20high%20temperatures%20may%20have%20derailed%20country%E2%80%99s%20E20%20action%20plans%2C%20hopefully%20for%20a%20short%20period%20only.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20December%207%20decision%20regarding%20use%20of%20molasses%20for%20ethanol%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdfpd.gov.in%2FLwB3AHIAaQB0AGUAcgBlAGEAZABkAGEAdABhAC8AUABvAHIAdABhAGwALwBOAGUAdwBzAC8A745_1_Supply_of_ethanol_from_sugar_and_molasses_based_distilleries.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eletter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Indian%20sugar%20mills%20and%20distilleries%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20(DFPD)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20nodal%20agency%20for%20sugar%20policies%20in%20India%2C%20invoked%20provisions%20of%20the%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%2C%201955%20(ECA)%20to%20direct%20two%20changes%3A%20(i)%20ban%20use%20of%20sugarcane%20juice%20and%20syrup%20for%20ethanol%20production%3B%20and%20(ii)%20restrict%20ethanol%20produced%20from%20B-heavy%20molasses%20to%20already%20contracted%20quantities.%20These%20apply%20to%20ethanol%20supply%20year%20(ESY)%202023-24%20(i.e.%2C%20November%202023%20to%20October%202024).%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20we%20deduce%20two%20things%20from%20this%3A%20(i)%20apart%20from%20grains%2C%20ethanol%20is%20mainly%20to%20come%20from%20the%20C-heavy%20molasses%20route%20in%20ESY%202023-24%2C%20and%20(ii)%20with%20smaller%20cane-based%20feedstock%2C%20ethanol%20blending%20performance%20this%20year%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20below%20the%20levels%20of%20E12%20in%20ESY%202022-23.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20case%20of%20B-heavy%2C%20the%20government%20has%20permitted%20the%20quantities%20already%20contracted%20by%20oil%20companies%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20supplied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021-22%2C%202.36%20billion%20litres%20of%20B-heavy%20based%20ethanol%20was%20supplied%20to%20oil%20companies.%20In%202022-23%2C%20this%20fell%20to%202.27%20billion%20litres.%20In%202023-24%2C%20in%20light%20of%20a%20smaller%20sugarcane%20crop%2C%20quantities%20contracted%20by%20oil%20companies%20have%20fallen%20to%201.3%20billion%20litres.%20The%20government%20has%20pegged%20the%20annual%20supplies%20from%20B-heavy%20to%20this%20quantity%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECentrality%20of%20sugarcane%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20E20%20initiative%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reduce%20country%E2%80%99s%20imported%20crude%20oil%20dependence%2C%20in%202018%20the%20government%20released%20its%20national%20policy%20on%20biofuels.%20Later%20in%202021%2C%20NITI%20Aayog%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20roadmap%20for%20achieving%20targets%20under%20the%20policy.%20Through%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farcusresearch.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FEthanol-blending-of-petrol-in-India-APR-.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eensuing%20journeys%20of%20the%20two%20documents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20it%20stands%20today%2C%20the%20country%20aims%20to%20achieve%2020%25%20blending%20in%20its%20fuel%20oil%20by%20year%202025-26.%20This%20target%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20E20%2C%20which%20implies%20that%20by%202025%2C%20a%20litre%20of%20fuel%20oil%20we%20would%20buy%20for%20our%20vehicles%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20200%20ml%20of%20ethanol%20and%20800%20ml%20of%20petroleum%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fenergy%2Fwith-the-climate-crisis-on-e10-might-be-indias-ethanol-blending-sweet-spot%2F%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20Climate%20Crisis%20On%2C%20E10%20Might%20Be%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ethanol-Blending%20Sweet%20Spot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2021-06%2FEthanolBlendingInIndia_compressed.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENITI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Ayog%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20to%20achieve%20E20%2C%20country%20is%20likely%20to%20need%20about%2010.16%20billion%20litres%20of%20ethanol%20annually.%20It%20projected%20that%20close%20to%2050%25%20of%20this%20ethanol%20is%20to%20be%20produced%20from%20sugarcane%20derivatives%20and%20the%20remaining%20half%20is%20to%20come%20from%20grains%20like%20rice%20released%20by%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%2C%20broken%20rice%20from%20the%20open%20market%2C%20and%20maize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20ESY%202022-23%2C%20the%20country%20achieved%20E12%20(12%25%20blending)%20which%20was%20the%20target%20for%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20produced%20about%204.94%20billion%20litres%20of%20ethanol%20of%20which%20about%2075%25%20came%20from%20sugarcane-based%20sources%2C%2015%25%20from%20rice%20released%20by%20FCI%2C%204%25%20from%20maize%20and%20the%20remaining%205%25%20came%20from%20damaged%20food%20grains%2C%20including%20broken%20rice%20from%20open%20market.%20Within%20cane-based%20sources%2C%2063%25%20came%20from%20B-heavy%20molasses%20and%2035%25%20from%20juice.%20Sugarcane%20based%20ethanol%20production%20was%20projected%20to%20remain%20the%20mainstay%20of%20the%20ethanol%20production%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20also%20envisaged%20that%20grain-based%20ethanol%20production%20would%20rise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EFigure%201%3A%20Contribution%20of%20cane-based%20feedstock%20in%20ESY%2022-23%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10200414%2Funnamed.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10200414%2Funnamed.png%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10200414%2Funnamed-293x300.png%20293w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688519%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20MOPNG.%20Data%20for%202022-23%20is%20till%20mid-October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EWhy%20is%20there%20a%20panic%20on%20sugarcane%20crop%3F%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20sugarcane%20crop%20in%202023-24%20has%20suffered%20on%20account%20of%20volatile%20monsoon%20rains.%20Parts%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Findia-working-prevent-disruption-ethanol-supplies-gasoline-blending-2023-12-08%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuffered%20significant%20losses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20cane%20yields%20and%20acreages.%20As%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupag.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20sugarcane%20production%20in%202023-24%20is%20estimated%20at%20435%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20(MMTs)%20which%20is%20about%2056%20MMTs%20lower%20than%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20491%20MMTs.%20This%20implies%20that%20compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20country%E2%80%99s%20sucrose%20production%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20by%206%20MMTs%20(at%2011%25%20recovery%20rate).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20current%20year%2C%20opening%20stocks%20of%20sugar%20on%20October%201%2C%202023%20were%20about%205.7%20MMTs%20and%20with%20production%20shortfall%20of%206%20MMTs%2C%20the%20supply%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20short%20of%20demand%20(about%2029%20MMTs)%20by%20about%202%20MMTs%20in%20the%20current%20year%2C%202023-24.%20Not%20surprisingly%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fforeign-trade%2Findian-govt-extends-restriction-on-sugar-exports-beyond-oct-31%2Farticleshow%2F104517217.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20government%20banned%20sugar%20exports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20early%20in%20the%20year.%20By%20manoeuvring%20the%20ethanol%20production%20away%20from%20sugarcane-derivatives%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20sucrose%20diversion%20to%20ethanol%20by%20about%202%20MMTs%20(calculated%20as%20back-of-envelope%20calculations).%20This%20may%20imply%20that%20the%20country%20could%20see%20through%20the%20next%20year%20with%20similar%20levels%20of%20inter-year%20stocks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20ESY%202023-24%2C%20the%20country%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2021-06%2FEthanolBlendingInIndia_compressed.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaimed%20to%20achieve%20ethanol%20blending%20target%20of%20E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20appears%20inevitable%20that%20the%20performance%20will%20fall%20short%20of%20this%20target.%20With%20lower%20availability%20of%20molasses-based%20feedstock%2C%20and%20poorer%20availability%20of%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20maize%2C%20maintaining%20current%20year%E2%80%99s%20E12%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%20in%20ESY%202023-24.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ethanol%20blending%20program%20is%20important%20in%20the%20larger%20scheme%20of%20things.%20While%20the%20country%20works%20to%20develop%20its%20crop%E2%80%99s%20resilience%20to%20droughts%20and%20pests%2C%20the%20need%20for%20improvement%20in%20crop%20yields%2C%20especially%20for%20maize%2C%20is%20absolutely%20urgent.%20The%20commercial%20production%20of%20second%20generation%20ethanol%20at%20viable%20rates%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20tested.%20If%20it%20is%20successful%20it%20can%20reduce%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fstubble-burning-problem-solutions-9033982%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estubble%20burning%20incidents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShweta%20Saini%20is%20an%20agricultural%20economist%20and%20CEO%2C%20Arcus%20Policy%20Research%20and%20Siraj%20Hussain%20is%20former%20Union%20agriculture%20secretary%2C%20GOI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702219781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10201346%2Fsugarcane-farmer-in-a-queue-waiting-to-sell_Alamy_2HM25XN-1800x1201-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findia-is-likely-to-miss-its-ethanol-blending-target-this-year%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20NITI%20Ayog%2C%20to%20achieve%20E20%2C%20the%20country%20is%20likely%20to%20need%20about%2010.16%20billion%20litres%20of%20ethanol%20annually%20with%20sugarcane%20based%20ethanol%20as%20the%20mainstay%20of%20production.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findia-is-likely-to-miss-its-ethanol-blending-target-this-year%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Children%20of%20jailed%20mother%20accept%20her%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702218360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-narges-mohammadi-ali-rahmani_6388675.jpg%3F20231210143429%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fteenage-children-of-jailed-iranian-activist-narges-mohammadi-accept-her-nobel-peace-prize-13027330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20children%20of%20jailed%20Iranian%20activist%20Narges%20Mohammadi%20have%20accepted%20this%20year's%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20on%20her%20behalf%20at%20a%20ceremony%20in%20Oslo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fteenage-children-of-jailed-iranian-activist-narges-mohammadi-accept-her-nobel-peace-prize-13027330%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fteenage-children-of-jailed-iranian-activist-narges-mohammadi-accept-her-nobel-peace-prize-13027330%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fteenage-children-of-jailed-iranian-activist-narges-mohammadi-accept-her-nobel-peace-prize-13027330%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chhattisgarh%3A%20BJP%20Ends%20Week-Long%20Suspense%2C%20Names%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20as%20Next%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10192940%2FGA6N65IaQAAU8Yf.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20a%20week%20of%20deliberation%2C%20and%20after%20appointment%20of%20three%20observers%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20finally%20named%20former%20Union%20minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20their%20chief%20minister%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20Senior%20tribal%20leader%20and%20a%20crowd%20favourite%2C%20the%20Kunkuri%20MLA%20is%20a%20four-time%20MP%20and%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20from%20Jashpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201964%20in%20Jashpur%20district%E2%80%99s%20Bagia%20village%2C%20Sai%20started%20his%20political%20career%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201989.%20Hailing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20politicians%2C%20Sai%20is%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20His%20uncle%20Narhari%20Prasad%20Sai%20served%20as%20a%20two%20time%20MLA%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Jan%20Sangh%20and%20was%20a%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%20Janata%20Party%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20too%20became%20a%20central%20government%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%202014%20Modi%20government%20and%20was%20entrusted%20with%20portfolios%20like%20steel%2C%20mining%20and%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20BJP%20lost%20Chhattisgarh%20in%202018%2C%20Sai%20was%20made%20the%20BJP%20state%20chief.%20On%20the%20international%20day%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20indigenous%20people%20last%20year%2C%20Sai%20was%20sacked%20from%20the%20post%20earning%20BJP%20heavy%20criticism.%20He%20was%20replaced%20by%20Arun%20Sao%2C%20an%20OBC%20face%20brought%20forward%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20counter%20former%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20OBC-politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20Kanwar%20tribe%2C%20Sai%20had%20declared%20property%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%203%20crore%20in%20the%20just%20concluded%20state%20election.%20Within%20the%20party%2C%20he%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20disciplined%20BJP%20leader%20and%20a%20Sangh%20loyalist.%20His%20name%20had%20been%20in%20the%20running%20since%20BJP%20won%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20results%20declared%20on%20December%203%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2054%20out%20of%2090%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%2017%20of%20the%2029%20tribal%20seats.%20After%20the%20tough%20line%20followed%20by%20Congress%20on%20the%20OBC%20card%2C%20many%20within%20the%20BJP%20thought%20that%20the%20the%20party%20would%20follow%20suit%20and%20name%20an%20OBC%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20political%20experts%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20played%20the%20tribal%20card%20as%20part%20of%20a%20bigger%20political%20narrative%20the%20it%20is%20building%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20has%20a%20tribal%20president%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20known%20to%20be%20rife%20with%20tribal%20issues.%20It%20makes%20complete%20sense%20to%20put%20a%20tribal%20CM%20in%20the%20state.%20Especially%2C%20from%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%20over%20the%20years%20felt%20neglected%20in%20the%20larger%20political%20narrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20political%20analyst%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20who%20was%20encouraged%20by%20Dilip%20Singh%20Judev%20to%20join%20politics%2C%20had%20managed%20to%20be%20close%20to%20former%20Chattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Raman%20Singh%20as%20well.%20In%20a%20fractured%20party%2C%20Sai%20had%20managed%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20good%20books%20of%20most%20leaders.%20This%2C%20many%20believe%2C%20will%20come%20in%20handy%20for%20him%20in%20handling%20the%20various%20factions%20simmering%20within%20the%20majority%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Sai%E2%80%99s%20appointment%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20setting%20the%20narrative%20for%20a%20new%20batch%20of%20leaders%20for%20Chhattisgarh.%20Within%20this%20new%20crop%2C%20the%20party%20seems%20to%20be%20instilling%20a%20kind%20of%20discipline%2C%20a%20perceived%20sense%20that%20positions%20of%20power%20come%20to%20those%20who%20wait%20diligently%20and%20work%20silently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Sai%20is%20a%20tribal%20face%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20has%20always%20put%20the%20party%20before%20his%20identity.%20In%20fact%2C%20tribal%20leaders%20believe%20that%20since%20he%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20political%20career%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20he%20has%20a%20certain%20disconnect%20from%20the%20tribal%20issues%20of%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20announced%20Vijay%20Sharma%20and%20Arun%20Sao%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20and%20Raman%20Singh%20as%20the%20speaker%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20while%20the%20suspense%20over%20who%20will%20bag%20the%20posts%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20continues.%20However%2C%20by%20choosing%20a%20tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20BJP%20certainly%20hopes%20to%20win%20brownie%20points%20in%20identity%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702216854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10192940%2FGA6N65IaQAAU8Yf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-bjp-ends-week-long-suspense-names-vishnu-deo-sai-as-next-chief-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Sai's%20appointment%2C%20t