0Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20government%20(2008-2022).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-news-nawaz-sharif-wanted-better-relations-with-india-was-ousted-for-opposing-kargil-101702116041011.html%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sharif%20also%20restated%20his%20call%20for%20demanding%20accountability%20of%20former%20military%20generals%20and%20judges%20for%20ruining%20Pakistan%20by%20overthrowing%20his%20government%20in%202017%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20brought%20this%20country%20to%20this%20level%20should%20be%20made%20accountable%20as%20patriotic%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20to%20their%20country.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20come%20into%20power%20to%20roam%20around%20in%20luxury%20cars%20but%20we%20want%20accountability%20of%20those%20(who)%20ruined%20this%20country%20and%20made%20false%20cases%20against%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202006%2C%20General%20Musharraf%2C%20in%20his%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20Line%20of%20Fire%3A%20A%20Memoir%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20had%20referred%20to%20this%20disagreement%20with%20Sharif%20on%20Kargil%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fworld%2Fkargil-episode-brought-musharraf-and-sharif-on-collision-course-1188094.html%5C%22%3Estating%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kargil%20episode%20created%20the%20biggest%20divide%20(between%20the%20two).%20We%20had%20both%20wanted%20to%20put%20Kashmir%20firmly%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20radar%20screen%2C%20politically%20as%20well%20as%20militarily%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20when%20%E2%80%9Cexternal%20political%20pressure%20forced%20Sharif%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20he%20broke%20down.%20%E2%80%9CRather%20than%20deriving%20strength%20through%20national%20solidarity%2C%20he%20(Sharif)%20blamed%20the%20Army%20and%20tried%2