e%20Unions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Frailways.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistoriography%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20independence%20is%20indeed%20an%20area%20that%20does%20not%20cease%20to%20grow%3B%20from%20nationalist%20narratives%20and%20Marxist%20analysis%2C%20the%20field%20has%20expanded%2C%20in%20a%20substantive%20sense%2C%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20post-colonial%20approach%20to%20nation%20and%20nationalism.%20Aniruddha%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20book%20is%20an%20addition%20to%20this%20school.%20Meanwhile%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20resist%20calling%20this%20work%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20post-modernist%20school%20and%20one%20without%20a%20sense%20of%20direction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20355px)%2085vw%2C%20355px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10151054%2F81Q-HeNoBEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22355%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10151054%2F81Q-HeNoBEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20667w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10151054%2F81Q-HeNoBEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-200x300.jpg%20200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688477%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAniruddha%20Bose%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EShunting%20the%20Nation%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20Railway%20Workers%20and%20the%20Most%20Tumultuous%20Decade%20in%20Modern%20Indian%20History%20(1939-1949)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ESpeaking%20Tiger%20Books%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202023%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBose%20has%20attempted%20to%20locate%20the%20organised%20work-force%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20partition%20and%20even%20while%20he%20has%20managed%20to%20narrate%20the%20partition%2C%20which%20a%20host%20of%20scholars%20have%20done%20with%20far%20more%20felicity%2C%20his%20treatment%20of%20the%20railway%20workers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20mainstay%20of%20his%20work%20as%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20title%20would%20convey%20%E2%80%93%20is%20far%20too%20sketchy%20and%20based%20on%20a%20limited%20set%20of%20sources.%20The%20author%20ends%20up%20repeating%20facts%20too%20often%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20reader%20is%20left%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20fatigue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Bose%20ought%20to%20be%20commended%20for%20taking%20up%20a%20study%20involving%20the%20working%20class%20and%20the%20national%20movement%2C%20a%20subject%20that%20gained%20traction%20in%20the%201980s%20in%20the%20Indian%20academia%20but%20began%20losing%20out%20to%20the%20postmodernist%20onslaught%20on%20history%2C%20his%20treatment%20of%20the%20subject%20leaves%20much%20to%20be%20desired.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBose%2C%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20looks%20at%20the%20workers%20in%20the%20railways%20as%20their%20own%20agents%20rather%20than%20locating%20their%20agency%20in%20the%20political%20leadership%20of%20the%20trade%20unions%3B%20for%20reasons%20known%20best%20to%20him.%20He%20does%20not%20even%20care%20to%20mention%20the%20existence%20of%20such%20agencies%2C%20that%20operated%20in%20the%20world%20of%20trade%20unions%2C%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3EAll%20India%20Trade%20Union%20Congress%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20predominance%20of%20the%20communists%20in%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20erasure%20of%20this%20record%2C%20in%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20study%2C%20is%20indeed%20a%20conscious%20choice%20and%20not%20due%20to%20ignorance.%20With%20this%2C%20Bose%20attempts%20hard%20to%20attribute%20to%20the%20railway%20worker%20some%20sort%20of%20consciousness%2C%20of%20the%20highest%20level%2C%20displayed%20during%20the%20war%20efforts%3B%20Bose%20simply%20states%20that%20even%20while%20sympathising%20with%20the%20call%20for%20Quit%20India%20and%20the%20national%20struggle%2C%20the%20workers%20as%20a%20class%20contributed%20in%20a%20big%20way%20to%20the%20war%20against%20fascism.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trouble%20with%20this%20approach%20is%20that%20such%20facts%20as%20the%20communists%20calling%20the%20war%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpeoples%E2%80%99%20war%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20was%20attacked%20by%20Germany%20(in%20the%20summer%20of%201941)%20is%20not%20even%20recorded%20by%20the%20author%20in%20his%20enthusiasm%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20postmodern%20version%20of%20the%20subaltern%20school.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%20book%20skirts%20an%20important%20phase%20in%20the%20trade%20union%20movement%E2%80%99s%20history%20involving%20the%20communists%20as%20much%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20war%20years%20were%20indeed%20when%20the%20communist%20leadership%20of%20the%20trade%20union%20movement%2C%20especially%20in%20most%20railway%20companies%20across%20India%2C%20won%20successful%20battles%20to%20institutionalise%20the%20concept%20of%20Dearness%20Allowance%20and%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20grain%20shops.%20Although%20the%20author%20goes%20into%20these%20and%20even%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20details%20on%20these%20aspects%2C%20he%20fails%20to%20locate%20these%20in%20context%3A%20the%20colonial%20state%2C%20the%20communist%20unions%20and%20the%20changing%20face%20of%20the%20war.%20This%20important%20aspect%20in%20several%20works%20of%20labour%20history%20seems%20non-existent%20for%20Bose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%20author%20weaves%20the%20whole%20account%20using%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Csurvival%20strategies%E2%80%9D%2C%20something%20that%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20labour%20history%20as%20such.%20And%20this%20gets%20so%20conspicuously%20out%20of%20place%20with%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20penchant%20to%20locate%20class%20consciousness%20without%20any%20trace%20of%20mediation%20or%20intervention%20by%20the%20trade%20unions%20and%20their%20political%20leadership%2C%20especially%20the%20communists.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBose%20seems%20alright%20with%20the%20non-communist%20leadership%20of%20the%20All-India%20Railwaymens%E2%80%99%20Federation%3B%20reading%20this%20account%20could%20lead%20someone%20to%20carry%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20communists%20did%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20trade%20union%20scene%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%3B%20this%20is%20contrary%20to%20facts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBose%20then%20takes%20recourse%20to%20a%20common%20argument%20in%20postmodern%20scholarship%20on%20labour%20and%20resistance%20%E2%80%93%20to%20treat%20stealing%20and%20shirking%20work%20as%20forms%20of%20resistance.%20While%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20substance%20in%20this%2C%20and%20British%20historian%20Eric%20Hobsbawm%20has%20theorised%20this%20(banditry%20as%20resistance)%2C%20the%20problem%20with%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20here%20is%20to%20locate%20resistance%20in%20only%20such%20acts%20and%20that%20too%20in%20a%20period%20(1939-1949)%20when%20the%20trade%20unions%20were%20pretty%20much%20in%20a%20position%20that%20influenced%20and%20guided%20the%20everyday%20resistance%20of%20the%20industrial%20working%20class%20in%20India%20and%20even%20hegemonised%20the%20nationalist%20leadership%20in%20many%20ways.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBose%2C%20however%2C%20misses%20out%20the%20historical%20context%20while%20dealing%20with%20an%20important%20aspect%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20struggle%20%E2%80%93%20the%20unions%20and%20the%20communists%20%E2%80%93%20and%20ends%20up%20relying%20on%20an%20account%20by%20a%20railway%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20D.V.%20Reddy%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20approach%20is%20evidently%20one%20of%20contempt%20to%20the%20workers.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20Aniruddha%20Bose%20could%20have%20profited%20reading%20existing%20works%20in%20labour%20history%20and%20the%20book%20under%20review%20would%20have%20been%20very%20different.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EV.%20Krishna%20Ananth%2C%20teaches%20History%20at%20the%20Sikkim%20Central%20University%2C%20Gangtok.%20He%20has%20researched%20on%20the%20trade%20unions%20and%20the%20national%20struggle%20for%20independence%20and%20his%20doctoral%20thesis%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20Historical%20Studies%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20is%20on%20this.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702206005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Frailways.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhy-the-role-of-trade-unions-cant-be-overlooked-in-a-book-on-the-indian-railways%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20'Shunting%20the%20Nation'%2C%20the%20mainstay%20of%20the%20author's%20work%20is%20far%20too%20sketchy%20and%20based%20on%20a%20limited%20set%20of%20sources.%20The%20author%20ends%20up%20repeating%20facts%20too%20often%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20reader%20is%20left%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20fatigue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhy-the-role-of-trade-unions-cant-be-overlooked-in-a-book-on-the-indian-railways%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20group%20to%20spend%20Rs%207%20trn%20in%20capex%20over%20next%20ten%20years%20across%20verticals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702204607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F28%2Ffull%2F1690511737-6386.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-group-to-sp