does%20not%20regard%20the%20Palestinian%20organisation%20as%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Lekhi%20went%20public%20to%20say%20she%20had%20not%20signed%20any%20such%20answer%2C%20the%20MEA%20issued%20an%20official%20clarification%20that%20a%20technical%20error%20had%20led%20to%20the%20answer%20being%20issued%20in%20her%20name%20instead%20of%20that%20of%20her%20ministerial%20colleague%2C%20V.%20Muraleedharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20official%20view%20and%20Lekhi%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20actions%20raise%20questions%20about%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20about%20how%20decisions%20are%20made%20and%20what%20its%20own%20ministers%20think%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20it%20matter%20which%20of%20the%20individual%20ministers%20in%20the%20same%20ministry%20signed%20an%20official%20answer%3F%20Is%20this%20the%20respect%20ministers%20have%20for%20their%20government%E2%80%99s%20views%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeenakshi%20Lekhi%20is%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20same%20government%20as%20the%20one%20that%20has%20answered%20the%20question%2C%20asking%20whether%20India%20believed%20that%20Hamas%20was%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%20%E2%80%9CDesignation%20of%20an%20organisation%20as%20terrorist%20is%20covered%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20declaring%20any%20organisation%20as%20terrorist%20is%20considered%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%20by%20the%20relevant%20government%20departments%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20answer%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Unstarred%20Question%20No.%20980%2C%20on%20December%208%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELekhi%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20no%20less%2C%20distanced%20herself%20from%20the%20question.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20signed%20any%20paper%20with%20this%20question%20and%20this%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20error%E2%80%9D%20could%20have%20been%20sorted%20out%20quietly%20and%20internally.%20Did%20it%20require%20Lekhi%20holding%20a%20political%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20error%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20soon%20after%20Lekhi%20created%20a%20fuss%2C%20and%20held%20a%20political%20press%20conference%20against%20her%20own%20ministry%20and%20said%20there%20would%20be%20a%20hunt%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cculprit%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20press%20conference%20suggests%20dissonance%20and%20confusion.%20Do%20all%20ministers%20not%20hold%20the%20same%20view%20as%20the%20Union%20government%20does%3F%20This%20is%20a%20government%20that%20prescribes%20%E2%80%9Cone%E2%80%9D%20of%20everything.%20Surely%2C%20all%20ministers%20can%20be%20held%20to%20%E2%80%9Cone%E2%80%9D%20view%20on%20such%20an%20important%20matter%3F%20Is%20%3Cem%3Eek%20sarkar%2C%20ek%20jawaab%3C%2Fem%3E%20too%20much%20to%20expect%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20are%20decisions%20made%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELekhi%20tagged%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20publicly%20on%20X.%20There%20was%20another%20tweet%20that%20asked%20about%20the%20official%20website%20of%20MEA%20uploading%20the%20question.%20The%20tweet%20questioned%20if%20Lekhi%20didn%E2%80%99t%20prepare%20the%20question%2C%20who%20did.%20Responding%20to%20this%20question%2C%20Lekhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20inquiry%20will%20reveal%20the%20culprit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EV.%20Muraleedharan%20serves%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20responsible%20for%20Gulf%20states%2C%20excluding%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%20Consequently%2C%20queries%20pertaining%20to%20this%20region%20typically%20bear%20his%20signature.%20If%20Lekhi%20identified%20a%20parliamentary%20question%20associated%20with%20a%20portfolio%20outside%20her%20purview%2C%20she%20could%20easily%20consult%20with%20her%20colleague%20looking%20after%20that%20region%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20%E2%80%98mistake%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELekhi%E2%80%99s%20public%20tweets%C2%A0speaks%20poorly%20of%20internal%20discussion%20mechanisms%20within%20a%20government%20that%20should%20know%20better.%20Coalition%20governments%20are%20sneered%20at%20for%20ministers%20expressing%20their%20own%20views%2C%20contrary%20to%20that%20held%20by%20governments.%20This%20tells%20its%20own%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EInquiry%20will%20reveal%20the%20culprit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DrSJaishankar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPMOIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PMOIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXPpfrlaUQ3%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXPpfrlaUQ3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Meenakashi%20Lekhi%20(%40M_Lekhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FM_Lekhi%2Fstatus%2F1733202924858458521%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20this%20government%20believe%20in%20collective%20responsibility%3F%20Or%20not%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2075(3)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20spells%20out%20collective%20responsibility%20in%20clear%20and%20uncertain%20terms.%20The%20clause%20reads%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20shall%20be%20collectively%20responsible%20to%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20Lekhi%20responding%20to%20the%20political%20embarrassment%20of%20publicly%20saying%20Hamas%20is%20not%20a%20terrorist%20group%20when%20her%20party%20and%20even%20the%20government%20has%20gone%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20support%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Gaza%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Palestine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20earlier%20today%20(December%2010)%2C%20Modi%2C%20anxious%20to%20keep%20up%20a%20sense%20of%20a%20special%20relationship%20with%20Israel%2C%20and%20especially%20his%20discredited%20counterpart%2C%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20is%20increasingly%20coming%20under%20pressure.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20on%20Gaza%20and%20thousands%20of%20civilian%20deaths%20have%20led%20to%20a%20sea%20change%20in%20global%20public%20opinion%20on%20unilaterally%20supporting%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20urging%20India%20to%20ban%20Hamas.%20Recently%2C%20its%20ambassador%20Naor%20Gilon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-asks-india-to-declare-hamas-as-a-terrorist-organisation%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20with%20Israel%20banning%20terrorist%20organisation%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%20which%20it%20did%2015%20years%20after%20the%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20India%20should%20also%20designate%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terror%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20taken%20an%20ambiguous%20stand%20with%20regard%20to%20Hamas%20over%20the%20years%20and%20it%20is%20not%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20group.%20Something%20that%20the%20reply%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20also%20outlined.%20It%20has%20cited%20the%20UN%20as%20a%20guide%2C%20proscribing%20organisations%20that%20have%20officially%20been%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20international%20body%2C%20which%20does%20not%20designate%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terrorist%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20despite%20the%20%E2%80%9Creflexive%20Hindutva%20embrace%20of%20Zionism%E2%80%9D%20about%20which%20much%20has%20been%20visible%20in%20the%20public%20for%20a%20while%20and%20documented%2C%20it%20has%20become%20difficult%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20ban%20Hamas%2C%20even%20if%20they%20want%20to%2C%20without%20seriously%20jeopardising%20other%20important%20economic%20and%20strategic%20interests%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20this%20government%20has%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20for%20designated%20UAPA%20courts%20to%20uphold%20a%20ban%20on%20Hamas%2C%20were%20it%20to%20be%20banned%20domestically%2C%20India%20would%20have%20to%20share%20evidence%20of%20involvement%20of%20the%20organisation%20in%20terror%20activities%20within%20India.%20So%20far%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702204259000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10152334%2Fimage-1589.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-meenakshi-lekhis-public-meltdown-over-hamas-tells-us-about-the-modi-government%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20official%20view%20and%20Lekhi%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20actions%20raise%20questions%20about%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20about%20how%20decisions%20are%20made%20and%20what%20its%20own%20ministers%20think%20about%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-meenakshi-lekhis-public-meltdown-over-hamas-tells-us-about-the-modi-government%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Tussle%20Between%20Two%20Political%20Streams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04152208%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.21.24.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20won%20back%20three%20majority%20Hindu%20states%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20National%20Crime%20Registration%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20report%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20was%20published.%20It%20almost%20got%20lost%20in%20the%20din%20that%20followed%20the%20BJP%20sweeping%20three%20out%20of%20four%20states%20in%20the%20crucial%20Hindi%20belt.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20396px)%2085vw%2C%20396px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22396%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NCRB%20data%20gives%20us%20invaluable%20insights%20into%20the%20direction%20we%20are%20headed.%20It%20reports%20that%20the%20last%20two%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F45-rise-in-hate-speech-cases-over-past-2-yrs-ncrb-report%2Farticleshow%2F105766371.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehave%20recorded%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%2045%25%20rise%20in%20hate%20speech%20and%20other%20acts%20that%20deepen%20and%20promote%20enmity%20between%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20language%2C%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20and%20place%20of%20birth%20registered%20under%20IPC(153%20A).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20number%20of%20such%20cases%20reported%20has%20risen%20from%20993%20in%202021%20to%201%2C444.%20It%20is%20no%20accident%20that%20maximum%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech%20were%20reported%20from%20UP%20(217)%2C%20followed%20by%20Rajasthan%20(191)%20and%20Maharashtra%20(178).%20All%20these%20states%20have%20seen%20bitterly%20contested%20state%20elections%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20It%20is%20also%20notable%20that%20the%20number%20of%20hate%20crimes%20registered%20a%20peak%20in%20some%20northeastern%20states%20and%20in%20Telangana%2C%20which%20have%20had%20state%20elections%20recently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElections%20in%20India%20kindle%20extraordinary%20emotions%20and%20hopes.%20Winning%20an%20election%20is%20seen%2C%20among%20the%20contestants%2C%20equivalent%20to%20stumbling%20upon%20a%20treasure.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20trigger%20a%20process%20during%20which%20most%20winners%20speedily%20get%20rich%2C%20it%20also%20strengthens%20a%20sort%20of%20mystical%20conviction%20that%20it%20is%20all%20to%20be%20credited%20to%20%E2%80%98The%20Leader%E2%80%99%20looking%20upon%20the%20%E2%80%98Chosen%20Ones%E2%80%99%20with%20an%20eye%20of%20grace%20that%20elevates%20them%20above%20all%20others%20as%20infallible.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20photographs%20preserve%20such%20moments%20of%20teary-eyed%20joy%20and%20feet%20touching%20among%20showers%20of%20rose%20petals.%20Look%20at%20the%20faces%20and%20the%20background%20carefully.%20The%20vigour%2C%20glory%20and%20significance%20it%20confers%20upon%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20as%20the%20divine%20wind%20under%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20sails%20are%20obvious.%20Religion%20and%20a%20brilliantly%20aggressive%20leadership%2C%20both%20the%20winners%20and%20their%20voters%20are%20convinced%20that%20they%20have%20together%20created%20this%20period%20of%20accelerated%20expansion%2C%20winning%20coalition%20partners%20and%20influencing%20new%20voters%20from%20among%20the%20faithful.%20%3Cem%3EJai%20ho!%20Jai%20ho!%3C%2Fem%3E%20Such%20euphoria%20among%20the%20winners%20is%20a%20quintessentially%20Indian%20phenomena.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20before%20many%20begin%20to%20lament%20the%20degradation%20of%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Buddha%20and%20Gandhi%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20cast%20an%20honest%20look%20at%20our%20past%20where%20hate%20speech%2C%20bombast%20and%20revenge%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20have%20frequently%20moved%20hand%20in%20hand%20whenever%20empires%20were%20being%20built%20and%20razed%20from%20Saindhav%20Pradesh%20to%20Magadh%20or%20from%20Tungbhadra%20region%20to%20Calicut.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EKaushitaki%20Upanishad%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20tale%20about%20Indra%2C%20by%20then%20self-proclaimed%20king%20of%20kings%20among%20Aryan%20gods.%20He%20had%20Pratardan%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Divodas%2C%20as%20his%20sidekick.%20Pratardan%20helped%20Indra%20plan%20his%20first%20coup%20against%20his%20own%20father.%20%E2%80%9CO%20Son%20of%20Divodas%2C%E2%80%9D%20Indra%20drunk%20on%20this%20victory%2C%20tells%20his%20mate%20Pratardan%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20shall%20grant%20you%20a%20boon%20now.%20What%20is%20it%20to%20be%3F%E2%80%9D%20Pratardan%20gave%20the%20standard%20reply%2C%20saying%20he%20wanted%20nothing%20for%20himself%2C%20only%20love%20and%20welfare%20for%20all%20the%20people.%20Indra%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20Pratardan%20makes%20it%20clear%20how%20empire%20building%20is%20not%20about%20happiness%20and%20public%20welfare%2C%20but%20about%20raw%20power%20and%20merciless%20and%20sustained%20aggression%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20boon%20of%20power%20I%20give%20you%20is%20not%20for%20dispensing%20public%20welfare.%20Behold%2C%20I%20am%20The%20Truth.%20Study%20me%20closely%20for%20your%20own%20good.%20I%20have%20killed%20Tvashtr%2Ca%20the%20creator%20of%20the%20Vajra.%20I%20fed%20the%20band%20of%20Aroormaga%20monks%20to%20%3Cem%3ESalavrik%3C%2Fem%3E%20(dogs%20or%20wolves).%20I%20have%20broken%20up%20countless%20treaties%20made%20on%20earth%2C%20in%20sky%20and%20further%20up%20in%20heavens.%20But%20not%20a%20hair%20on%20my%20head%20was%20disturbed.%20If%20after%20receiving%20this%20wisdom%20from%20me%2C%20you%20can%20fathom%20the%20whys%20and%20wherefores%20of%20my%20acts%2C%20even%20if%20you%20go%20and%20murder%20your%20own%20kin%2C%20you%20shall%20cease%20to%20hesitate%20and%20not%20allow%20any%20emotions%20to%20cross%20your%20face%20ever%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-narrative-polls-bjp-hindutva%5C%22%3EDivided%20Cadre%2C%20Soft%20Hindutva%20and%20Other%20Factors%20That%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Help%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeace%20returned%20briefly%20to%20their%20valley.%20But%20such%20absolute%20power%20among%20gods%20and%20men%20is%20usually%20followed%20by%20hubris.%20The%20fall%20began.%20Indra%20lost%20out%20to%20the%20younger%20priest-led%20pantheon%20of%20Sanatan%20gods.%20Hari%20or%20Vishnu%20a%20Vaishnavite%20god%20joined%20the%20company%20of%20Hara%20(Shiva)%20and%20the%20coalition%20of%20Harihara%20was%20born.%20Enraged%20by%20the%20rising%20popularity%20of%20Krishna%2C%20now%20deemed%20the%20Avatara%20of%20Hari%2C%20Indra%20sent%20a%20terrible%20cloud%20burst%20to%20drown%20the%20region%20that%20defied%20his%20authority.%20At%20this%20Krishna%20is%20said%20to%20have%20picked%20up%20a%20whole%20mountain%20(Govardhan%20Parvat)%20on%20his%20little%20finger%20as%20an%20umbrella%20to%20protect%20his%20people%20and%20their%20herds%20and%20foiled%20the%20cyclonic%20deluge%20sent%20by%20an%20ageing%20Indra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKrishna%E2%80%99s%20own%20rise%20is%20associated%20with%20considerable%20violence%20after%20barely%20evading%20the%20efforts%20by%20uncle%20Kamsa%20to%20kill%20the%20infant%20born%20to%20jailed%20parents.%20As%20a%20teenager%2C%20he%20killed%20the%20royal%20tormentor%20of%20his%20parents%20and%20the%20killer%20of%20his%20siblings%20and%20proceeded%20to%20crown%C2%A0%20one%20of%20his%20close%20associates%20as%20king%20of%20Mathura.%20Then%20he%20got%20busy%20with%20his%20dream%20project%3A%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20of%20republics.%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20countless%20temples%20to%20him%2C%20none%20to%20Indra%2C%20now%20remembered%20only%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20festivals%20by%20a%20token%20flag%20(Indra%20Dhwaja)!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20the%20rise%20and%20fall%20of%20empires%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitical%20victories%20of%20the%20sort%20we%20have%20just%20seen%20are%20reminders%20that%20like%20Indra%2C%20like%20Krishna%20traumatised%20by%20an%20abusive%20childhood%2C%20leadership%20may%20often%20harbour%20a%20grudge%20resulting%20in%20reprisals%20and%20revenge.%20Recent%20mocking%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20their%20brilliant%20early%20leaders%20while%20celebrating%20victory%20of%20the%20party%20sweeps%20away%20the%20popular%20western%20games%20theory%2C%20according%20to%20which%20politics%20is%20like%20chess%2C%20complex%20but%20always%20played%20with%20inalienable%20rules.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETruth%20is%20in%20the%20wars%20for%20absolute%20power%2C%20each%20side%20fights%20for%20itself%2C%20with%20neither%20the%20referees%20nor%20the%20audiences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%2C%E2%80%9D%20Indra%20jauntily%20asks%20Pratardan%2C%20%E2%80%9Cexactly%20are%20rules%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98rights%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98wrongs%E2%80%99%20%3F%E2%80%9D%20Hadn%E2%80%99t%20he%2C%20the%20king%20of%20kings%20killed%20his%20own%20first%20contact%2C%20his%20chief%20arms%20dealer%20Tvashtra%20by%20his%20own%20hand%20without%20hesitating%20or%20allowing%20an%20emotion%20to%20cross%20his%20brow%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMyth%20proposes%2C%20action%20disposes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20generations%20our%20parents%20had%20handed%20us%20homilies%20about%20right%20and%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20civil%20speech%2C%20civil%20rights%2C%20and%20good%20manners.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20just%20handing%20out%20laptops%2C%20the%20internet%2C%20and%203D%20printers.%20The%20more%20gifted%20and%20curious%20among%20the%20millennials%2C%20like%20Indra%20in%20his%20time%2C%20will%20at%20some%20point%20access%20not%20only%20the%20darknet%20to%20hack%20archives%20and%20lives%20but%20also%20AI%20and%20sophisticated%20spyware%20destroying%20all%20those%20who%20may%20bear%20witness%20against%20them%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20this%2075-year%20journey%20as%20one%20nation%2C%20we%20are%20now%20facing%20a%20period%20when%20privileged%20star%20kids%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EArchies%3C%2Fem%3E%20reveal%20a%20generation%20that%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20all%20that%20s**t.%20English%20literacy%20and%20markets%20have%20created%20bubbles%20for%20the%20privileged%20where%20they%20live%20and%20love%20and%20have%20their%20being.%20Vision%202047%20means%20nothing%20to%20them.%20They%20are%2C%20like%20many%20grown%20ups%2C%20in%20denial%20about%20reality%3A%20environmentally%20driven%20migrations.%20The%20political%20dominance%20of%20the%20Delhi-led%20north%20pitted%20against%20a%20southern%20resistance%20from%20the%20highly%20literate%20and%20prosperous%20southern%20states.%20Punjab%20is%20slowly%20evaporating%20as%20an%20agricultural%20haven%20like%20Bihar%20did%20in%20the%2019th%20century.%20And%20more%20bedraggled%20semi-literate%20migrants%20will%20soon%20be%20streaming%20down%20south%20from%20the%20north.%20Will%20they%20leave%20any%20footprints%20in%20southern%20states%20other%20than%20Bhojpuri%20and%20Punjabi%20pop%2C%20full%20of%20more%20abusive%20words%20and%20images%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELanguage%20extinctions%20driven%20by%20social%20hubris%20and%20political%20spite%20and%20the%20confrontations%20over%20%E2%80%98imposition%E2%80%99%20of%20an%20artificial%20uniformity%20%E2%80%93%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Flag%2C%20One%20Law%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20alien%20to%20our%20democracy.%20And%20our%20people%20have%20always%20fiercely%20rejected%20the%20efforts%20at%20homogenisation%20of%20local%20cultures.%20The%20new%20North%20versus%20South%20debate%20is%20alarming%20because%20it%20signals%20a%20democratic%20environment%20increasingly%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20xenophobic%20intolerance%20of%20our%20smaller%20cultural%20republics.%20The%20only%20way%20to%20survive%20such%20toxicity%20is%20to%20pause%2C%20look%20back%20and%20make%20an%20honest%20assessment%20of%20our%20own%20past%20history%20of%20elections%2C%20of%20Indians%20from%20across%20the%20Wagah%20border%20and%20their%20culture%20and%20languages%20coming%20in%2C%20settling%20in%20happily%2C%20creating%20their%20own%20forms%20of%20pidgin%20dialects%20and%20enriching%20our%20and%20culture.%20It%20is%20the%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20year%20of%20our%20democracy%20and%20we%20are%20shrinking%20on%20many%20fronts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIti%20Varnavidah%20perhoornipunam%20tam%20nibodhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20words%20to%20the%20wise%20from%20the%20linguists.%20Try%20to%20make%20what%20you%20will%20out%20of%20them.)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPaniniya%20Shiksha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702202412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04152208%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.21.24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-tussle-between-two-political-streams%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20North%20versus%20South%20debate%20is%20alarming%20because%20it%20signals%20a%20democratic%20environment%20increasingly%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20xenophobic%20intolerance%20of%20our%20smaller%20cultural%20republics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-tussle-between-two-political-streams%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mizoram%3A%20BJP%20Falters%20in%20Power%20Bid%20Amid%20Hindutva%20Concerns%3B%20ZPM%20Emerges%20as%20a%20Force%20in%20Northeast%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08123037%2FScreenshot-2023-12-08-at-12.30.10%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20the%20new%20government%20in%20Mizoram%20completed%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20once%20again%20failed%20to%20share%20power%20in%20the%20government%20of%20this%20northeastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20despite%20the%20national%20party%20increasing%20its%20tally%20from%20just%20one%20in%202018%20to%20two%20seats%20in%20these%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20refused%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20pre-poll%20alliance%20with%20the%20national%20party%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20it%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20North%20East%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NEDA).%20In%20addition%2C%20after%20its%20massive%20win%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20accommodate%20the%20lone%20MLA%20who%20had%20won%20the%20first-ever%20seat%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%2040-member%20Mizoram%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20too%2C%20another%20regional%20entity%2C%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20embrace%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20government%20formation%2C%20even%20though%20it%20is%20understood%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%20than%20that%20of%20the%20MNF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20counting%20trends%20on%20December%204%20firmed%20up%2C%20state%20BJP%20president