D.%20On%20his%20first%20day%20at%20work%2C%20he%20also%20met%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Mizoram%20Church%20Leadership%20Committee%20alongside%20his%20party%20colleagues.%20On%20December%204%2C%20after%20ZPM%20swept%20the%20polls%2C%20a%20service%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20Church%20at%20its%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20November%207%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20pocketed%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20belt%20dominated%20by%20Mara%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20second%20largest%20community%2C%20who%2C%20too%2C%20belong%20to%20the%20Christian%20community.%20A%20local%20journalist%20told%20this%20correspondent%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20voters%20saw%20the%20BJP%20beyond%20Hindutva%20because%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20top%20leaders%2C%20who%20control%20the%20Mara%20Autonomous%20Council%2C%20and%20thereby%20have%20considerable%20say%20in%20an%20assembly%20election%2C%20have%20moved%20to%20the%20BJP.%20But%20for%20how%20long%20this%20love%20affair%20will%20continue%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20said%20for%20sure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Lalduhoma%20government%20taking%20over%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20administration%2C%20Mizoram%20has%2C%20thus%2C%20remained%20the%20only%20state%20where%20the%20ruling%20party%20under%20Modi%20is%20not%20part%20of%20a%20northeastern%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-election-results-usher-in-new-politics-and-developmental-challenges%5C%22%3EMizoram%20Election%20Results%20Usher%20in%20New%20Politics%20and%20Developmental%20Challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20chapter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20significant%20about%20these%20elections%20is%2C%20on%20December%208%2C%20with%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%2C%20this%20tiny%20border%20state%20not%20only%20formally%20recorded%20the%20blossoming%20of%20a%20new%20regional%20entity%20in%20ZPM%2C%20but%20also%20added%20a%20new%20chapter%20to%20the%20Northeast%E2%80%99s%20protracted%20sub-nationalist%20political%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2074%2C%20Lalduhoma%2C%20also%20the%20ZPM%20founder%2C%20might%20seem%20over-aged%20to%20lead%20a%20state%2C%20but%20he%20was%20the%20youngest%20among%20the%20Mizo%20leaders%20vying%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20in%20the%20November%207%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga%2C%20whom%20he%20unseated%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20is%2079.%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Lalsawta%2C%20who%20would%20have%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20and%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-eight-takeaways-zpm-mnf-bjp%5C%22%3Ehelped%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20get%20the%20numbers%20on%20December%204%2C%20is%2077.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20top%20Mizo%20leaders%2C%20since%20Mizoram%20became%20a%20state%20in%201987%2C%20only%20Laldenga%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20run%20was%20cut%20short%20at%2063%20due%20to%20lung%20cancer.%20After%20C.%20Chhunga%2C%20the%20first%20chief%20minister%20of%20Mizoram%20as%20a%20Union%20territory%20(UT)%2C%20Laldenga%20was%20undoubtedly%20its%20tallest%20leader%3B%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%2C%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20Mizo%20Accord%20of%201986%2C%20which%20brought%20down%20the%20curtain%20on%20its%20insurgency%20and%20made%20the%20UT%20India%E2%80%99s%2023rd%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20invincible%20MNF%20that%20ZPM%20had%20shown%20the%20door%20in%20a%20clean%20sweep%20in%20these%20elections.%20Since%20Laldenga%E2%80%99s%20demise%20in%201990%2C%20MNF%20had%20been%20led%20by%20Zoramthanga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZPM%2C%20an%20alliance%20of%20six%20regional%20entities%20hinged%20on%20Mizo%20sub-nationalism%2C%20may%20have%20risen%20to%20power%20now.%20However%2C%20in%202018%2C%20political%20observers%20had%20already%20noted%20its%20electoral%20presence.%20Faced%20with%20the%20anti-incumbency%20of%20a%20two-time%20Lal%20Thanhawla-led%20Congress%20government%2C%20which%20was%20then%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20both%20MNF%20and%20the%20BJP%20attempted%20to%20make%20Mizoram%20Congress-mukt%2C%20akin%20to%20other%20northeastern%20states.%20(Thanhawla%20was%20cumulatively%20the%20longest-serving%20chief%20minister%20of%20Mizoram.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZPM%20had%20jumped%20into%20the%20fray%2C%20too.%20However%2C%20having%20born%20only%20in%202017%2C%20its%20fundamentals%20were%20not%20in%20place.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20party%20symbol%20recognised%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Its%20candidates%20in%2035%20of%20the%2040%20constituencies%20that%20it%20contested%20had%20to%20fight%20as%20independents.%20Eight%20of%20them%2C%20led%20by%20Lalduhoma%2C%20got%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20ZPM%20became%20the%20second-largest%20party%2C%20without%20a%20party%20symbol%20it%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20become%20the%20largest%20opposition%20at%20that%20time.%20In%202018%2C%20too%2C%20the%20three-decades-old%20tradition%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20MNF%20sharing%20power%20in%20Mizoram%20alternately%20may%20have%20continued%2C%20but%20the%20tally%20indicated%20an%20implicit%20public%20sanction%20for%20a%20new%20regional%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20this%20indication%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20threat%20by%20the%20ruling%20MNF%20could%20be%20assessed%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20Lalduhoma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmizoram-mla-lalduhoma-the-first-lok-sabha-mp-to-be-disqualified-axed-again-for-defection-2331229%5C%22%3Ewas%20disqualified%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20assembly%20in%202020%20for%20having%20moved%20to%20ZPM%20formally%2C%20after%20the%20Commission%20recognised%20it%20as%20a%20political%20party.%20His%20disqualification%20came%20because%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resign%20as%20an%20independent%20before%20joining%20ZPM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Laldhuhoma%2C%20an%20IPS%20officer%20of%201974%20batch%2C%20it%20was%2C%20however%2C%20a%20second%20disqualification%20under%20the%20anti-defection%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20if%20a%20state%20satrap%20like%20Zoramthanga%20saw%20in%20him%20a%20political%20threat%2C%20precipitating%20his%20disqualification%20on%20technical%20grounds%2C%20he%20was%20also%20thrown%20out%20of%20parliament%20back%20in%201988%20after%20resigning%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20following%20a%20power%20tussle%20with%20another%20satrap%2C%20Lal%20Thanhawla.%20Lalduhoma%20thus%20became%20the%20first%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20to%20be%20disqualified%20under%20that%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20politics%20from%20bureaucracy%20was%20due%20to%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%3B%20she%20noticed%20him%20when%20he%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20her%20security.%20Her%20government%20utilised%20him%20in%20the%20Mizo%20peace%20process%20with%20Laldenga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20lateral%20entry%20from%20New%20Delhi%20into%20Mizo%20affairs%20was%20not%20taken%20lightly%20by%20chief%20minister%20Lal%20Thanhawla.%20He%20was%20sidelined%20in%20the%20state%20Congress%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20his%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20regionalist%20at%20heart%2C%20Lalduhoma%20went%20on%20to%20form%20a%20new%20party%2C%20Zoram%20Nationalist%20Party%20(ZNP)%3B%20became%20a%20ZNP%20MLA%2C%20too%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20grow%20it%20as%20a%20power%20to%20reckon%2C%20till%20it%20consolidated%20itself%20into%20ZPM.%20After%2025%20years%20of%20waiting%2C%20he%20finally%20became%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20MNF%20and%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20win%2C%20he%20reiterated%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20unification%20of%20the%20Zo-Kuki-dominated%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20into%20Mizoram%2C%20a%20demand%20that%20Laldenga%20had%20raised%20with%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20but%20failed%20due%20to%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20balkanize%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Lalduhoma%20government%20is%20keeping%20a%20distance%20from%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20most%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20pressure%20from%20the%20Church%20which%20has%20a%20considerable%20say%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20politics%2C%20since%202018%20though%2C%20he%20is%20widely%20known%20in%20the%20political%20circles%20of%20the%20state%20to%20have%20maintained%20good%20relations%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20times%20to%20come%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20that%20closeness%20of%20the%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20top%20leader%20with%20the%20BJP%20can%20also%20convince%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20help%20deliver%20that%20tall%20Zo-unification%20promise%20which%20Laldenga%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702200852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08123037%2FScreenshot-2023-12-08-at-12.30.10%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-bjp-falters-in-power-bid-amid-hindutva-concerns-zpm-emerges-as-a-force-in-northeast-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20Lalduhoma%20government%20taking%20over%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20administration%2C%20Mizoram%20has%20remained%20the%20only%20state%20where%20the%20ruling%20party%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20not%20part%20of%20a%20northeastern%20state%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-bjp-falters-in-power-bid-amid-hindutva-concerns-zpm-emerges-as-a-force-in-northeast-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20didn't%20sleep%20for%2049%20days'%3A%20Released%20hostages%20describe%20terror%20of%20Hamas%20captivity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170