%20the%20Act%20by%20the%20relevant%20government%20departments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20that%20perhaps%2C%20because%20the%20Israeli%20government%20was%20unhappy%20with%20the%20response%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20question%20was%20asked%2C%20Lekhi%20distanced%20herself%20from%20the%20question.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20signed%20any%20paper%20with%20this%20question%20and%20this%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20another%20tweet%20that%20asked%20about%20the%20official%20website%20of%20MEA%20uploading%20the%20question.%20The%20tweet%20questioned%20if%20Lekhi%20didn%E2%80%99t%20prepare%20the%20question%2C%20who%20did.%20Responding%20to%20this%20question%2C%20Lekhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20inquiry%20will%20reveal%20the%20culprit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20soon%20after%2C%20Lekhi%20told%20reporters%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20asked%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20to%20inquire%20and%20take%20action%20against%20those%20who%20put%20this%20question%20up%20against%20my%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20this%20issue%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20party%20as%20it%20was%20a%20government%20matter.%20On%20being%20asked%20if%20Hamas%20should%20be%20banned%2C%20she%20said%20the%20concerned%20division%20would%20answer%20on%20this%20matter.%20On%20questions%20as%20to%20how%20the%20question%20was%20also%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20website%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20asked%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20to%20get%20this%20%5Bquestion%5D%20removed.%20He%20has%20told%20me%20that%20once%20it%20is%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20website%2C%20certain%20procedures%20and%20amendments%20are%20required%20before%20the%20correction%20can%20be%20done.%20I%20have%20not%20signed%20any%20paper%20with%20this%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20their%20cue%2C%20the%20ministry%20decided%20to%20own%20up%20to%20the%20mistake%20soon%20after.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20noted%20that%20Lok%20Sabha%20Unstarred%20Question%20No.%20980%2C%20answered%20on%20December%208%2C%202023%2C%20needs%20a%20technical%20correction%20in%20terms%20of%20reflecting%20Shri%20V.%20Muraleedharan%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20replying%20to%20the%20parliament%20question.%20This%20is%20being%20suitably%20undertaken%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MEA%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Congress%20remained%20unconvinced.%20MP%20K.%20Sudhakaran%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20has%20always%20stood%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%20This%20flip%20flop%20is%20not%20only%20a%20breach%20of%20parliamentary%20privilege%2C%20but%20also%20a%20violation%20of%20oath%20of%20office%20by%20the%20minister%20under%20Article%2075%20of%20the%20constitution.%20The%20BJP%20has%20always%20had%20an%20ambiguous%20stand%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20In%20an%20effort%20to%20seek%20clarity%2C%20the%20question%20was%20put%20up.%20Now%20the%20minister%20says%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20sign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%2C%20too%2C%20raised%20some%20questions%20on%20X.%20%E2%80%9CAsking%20questions%20that%20were%20submitted%20by%20someone%20else%20led%20to%20the%20expulsion%20of%20an%20MP%20yesterday.%20Today%2C%20a%20minister%20denied%20that%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20PQ%20%5Bparliament%20question%5D%20was%20approved%20by%20her.%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20that%20be%20investigated%20too%3F%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20lead%20to%20seeking%20accountability%2C%20however%20innocuous%20the%20response%20from%20MEA%20may%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwatch-is-israel-determined-to-obliterate-hamas-no-matter-the-toll-of-palestinian-civilian-lives%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20Is%20Israel%20Determined%20to%20Obliterate%20Hamas%20No%20Matter%20the%20Toll%20of%20Palestinian%20Civilian%20Lives%3F%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fisrael-envoy-naor-gilon-calls-for-adding-hamas-to-indias-terror-list-its-time-to-11698552483574.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20nudging%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20to%20ban%20Hamas.%20Recently%2C%20ambassador%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-asks-india-to-declare-hamas-as-a-terrorist-organisation%5C%22%3ENaor%20Gilon%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fisrael-will-restart-gaza-bombings-once-hostage-release-ceasefire-end-envoy%2Farticle67583749.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20with%20Israel%20banning%20terrorist%20organisation%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%20India%2C%20too%2C%20should%20also%20designate%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terror%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20India%20had%20indicated%20to%20Israel%20whether%20it%20was%20considering%20a%20ban%20on%20Hamas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fisrael-pushes-india-for-hamas-ban-amid-arab-solidarity-show%2Farticleshow%2F105576805.cms%5C%22%3EGilon%20said%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20whatever%20was%20expected%20from%20our%20side.%20Now%2C%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20decide%20%E2%80%93%20if%2C%20where%2C%20how%2C%20how%20fast.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20India%20has%20taken%20an%20ambiguous%20stand%20with%20regard%20to%20Hamas%2C%20trying%20to%20keep%20positive%20relations%20with%20both%20the%20Arabs%20and%20Israel.%20It%20has%20taken%20refuge%20behind%20the%20UN%20by%20proscribing%20organisations%20that%20have%20officially%20been%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20international%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20for%20designated%20UAPA%20courts%20to%20uphold%20a%20ban%20on%20Hamas%20domestically%2C%20India%20would%20have%20to%20share%20evidence%20of%20involvement%20of%20the%20organisation%20in%20terror%20activities%20within%20India.%20So%20far%2C%20there%20is%20little%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702186038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F14215731%2FScreen-Shot-2020-01-14-at-9.57.09-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbjp-mp-meenakshi-lekhi-distances-herself-from-parliament-query-on-indias-stand-on-hamas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20said%20this%20issue%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20party%20as%20it%20was%20a%20government%20matter.%20On%20being%20asked%20if%20Hamas%20should%20be%20banned%2C%20she%20said%20the%20concerned%20division%20would%20answer%20on%20this%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbjp-mp-meenakshi-lekhi-distances-herself-from-parliament-query-on-indias-stand-on-hamas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explosion%20and%20fireball%20seen%20as%20storm%20sweeps%20through%20Tennessee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702185409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FC933%2Fproduction%2F_131970515_p0gyp0x2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67674135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tornadoes%20battering%20Tennessee%20leave%20thousands%20of%20people%20without%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-67674135%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airlines%20can%20save%20Rs%20150-180%20cr%20by%20using%20Eastern%20Cross%20Taxiways%3A%20DIAL%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702184649000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-05%2F02%2Ffull%2F1